# thoth_api_key

Issues short-lived scoped API keys.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_api_key" "agent_exec" {
  name            = "agent-exec"
  scope_level     = "agent"
  scope_target_id = "agent-123"
  permissions     = ["execute", "read"]
  ttl_seconds     = 3600
  jit_reason      = "incident-response"
}
```
